-- 1. Clínica Caro - Expat-focused healthcare
('Clínica Caro', 'Doctors', 'Private healthcare clinic in Valencia specializing in services for expats and international patients. Features English-speaking doctors and fast appointment scheduling, often within 48 hours. Provides direct access to specialists without endless referrals. Offers comprehensive services including endocrinology, cardiology, nutrition, and private medical checkups. Medical reports available in English for insurance purposes. Coordinates treatments and works with international health insurers to provide seamless care for expats living in or visiting Valencia.', 'Calle del Mar 18, 46003 Valencia', 'Valencia', 'Valencia', '+34 960 056 666', 'info@clinica-caro.com', 'https://clinica-caro.com', true, true, true, false, NOW(), NOW()),

-- 2. Hospital Quirónsalud Valencia - Major private hospital with English support
('Hospital Quirónsalud Valencia', 'Doctors', 'Leading private hospital in Valencia located in the historic Condes de Denia palace. Part of Spain''s largest private healthcare group with English-speaking staff and international patient services. Comprehensive medical and surgical specialties including cardiology, oncology, orthopedics, neurology, and fertility treatments. Modern facilities combined with historic architecture. International patient office assists with insurance coordination and multilingual support. Emergency services available 24/7.', 'Avda. Blasco Ibáñez 14, 46010 Valencia', 'Valencia', 'Valencia', '+34 963 690 600', 'valencia@quironsalud.es', 'https://www.quironsalud.com/valencia', true, true, true, false, NOW(), NOW()),

-- 3. Hospital IMED Valencia - International patient services
('Hospital IMED Valencia', 'Doctors', 'Private general hospital with English-speaking doctors and medical staff serving Valencia''s international community. Part of the IMED hospital group with multiple centers across Alicante and Valencia. Employs over 1,200 medical professionals with a dedicated international patient department. Full range of medical and surgical services with modern facilities. Coordinates care for expats and provides medical documentation in English for insurance and repatriation needs. Direct billing available for major international insurance providers.', 'Calle de la Cueva de Menga 4, 46021 Valencia', 'Valencia', 'Valencia', '+34 963 505 500', 'info@imedvalencia.com', 'https://www.imedvalencia.com', true, true, true, false, NOW(), NOW()),

-- 4. Vithas Hospital Nueve de Octubre - Private hospital with English support
('Vithas Hospital Nueve de Octubre', 'Doctors', 'Private hospital in Valencia with English-speaking staff and international patient services. Information, admissions, and most departments offer English language support. Comprehensive medical specialties including emergency care, surgery, maternity, and diagnostic imaging. International patient office provides assistance with appointments, insurance, and medical coordination. Modern facilities with patient-centered care approach for Valencia''s expat and international community.', 'Carrer de Valle de Ballestera 59, 46015 Valencia', 'Valencia', 'Valencia', '+34 963 179 100', 'internacional@vithas.es', 'https://www.vithas.es', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW()),

-- 5. International Doctor 24h Valencia - 24/7 House Call Service
('International Doctor 24h Valencia', 'Doctors', '24-hour English-speaking doctor service providing home visits and urgent care throughout Valencia. Specializes in medical care for tourists, expats, and international visitors who need immediate attention without language barriers. Doctors come directly to your home, hotel, or accommodation. Services include urgent care consultations, prescriptions, medical certificates, and coordination with hospitals if needed. Available 7 days a week including holidays for peace of mind when living in or visiting Valencia.', 'Servicio a domicilio en toda Valencia', 'Valencia', 'Valencia', '+34 900 909 533', 'info@internationaldoctor24h.com', 'https://internationaldoctor24h.com', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW()),

-- 6. Mobi Doctor Valencia - Online English-Speaking Doctors
('Mobi Doctor Valencia', 'Doctors', 'Online telemedicine service connecting Valencia residents and visitors with English-speaking doctors via video consultation. Quick and convenient medical care without waiting rooms or language barriers. Services include general consultations, prescriptions, medical advice, and sick notes. Consultations start at €29. Ideal for non-urgent medical issues, prescription refills, and general health questions. Available for tourists, digital nomads, and expats who need flexible healthcare access in Valencia.', 'Telemedicine - Online Consultations', 'Valencia', 'Valencia', '+34 960 056 545', 'support@mobidoctor.eu', 'https://www.mobidoctor.eu/doctors/valencia', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW()),

-- 7. Valencia Dental - English-Speaking Dentists
('Valencia Dental', 'Dentists', 'Modern dental clinic in Valencia with English-speaking dentists and staff catering to the international community. Comprehensive dental services including general dentistry, cosmetic dentistry, orthodontics, dental implants, and emergency dental care. Clear communication ensures patients fully understand treatment options and procedures. Comfortable, state-of-the-art facility with digital imaging and modern treatment technology. Accepts international dental insurance and provides detailed treatment plans in English.', 'Calle de la Paz 14, 46003 Valencia', 'Valencia', 'Valencia', '+34 963 511 222', 'info@valenciadental.es', NULL, true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW()),

-- 8. Dental Care Valencia - International Dental Clinic
('Dental Care Valencia', 'Dentists', 'International dental clinic specializing in services for expats, tourists, and English-speaking residents of Valencia. Team of experienced dentists fluent in English providing everything from routine checkups to complex restorative work. Services include cleanings, fillings, crowns, bridges, whitening, and dental emergencies. Patient-focused approach with detailed explanations of all procedures. Convenient central location with modern, comfortable facilities designed with international patients in mind.', 'Carrer de Colón 20, 46004 Valencia', 'Valencia', 'Valencia', '+34 963 520 000', 'appointments@dentalcarevalencia.com', NULL, true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
